            {
              "message": "`knowledge/adr/2026-06-26-0503-...` is not a resolvable path in a fresh checkout; this distributed capability doc now points at an abbreviated/nonexistent ADR reference instead of the concrete ADR file, so the cross-reference cannot be followed by consumers.",
